Date: Sat, 20 Jun 2026 20:51:55 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 09/21] feat(api): add live session sync subscription

Add a session subscribe SSE endpoint that emits a snapshot, catch-up
state, and replayable live run events for clients that drop into an
existing API session. Also expose lightweight live state on session list
and detail responses so clients can show active work without N+1 calls.

Co-authored-by: Nako <280596805+nakoagent@users.noreply.github.com>

